data.description: FHA ASSUMABLE LOAN AVAILABLE - 3.75% interest rate! Nestled within the beautiful Ventana community, this stunning 4-bedroom, 3 (full) bathroom house is a true gem. With an open floor plan designed for modern living, a spacious extended back patio for entertaining, and a large kitchen island that is the heart of the home. Each bedroom is generously sized, providing plenty of space for relaxation and personalization. This home has a bonus office nook that is great for remote working, craft space or homework area. Ventana isn't just a place to live; it's a lifestyle. Residents here have access to a resort style pool for hot summer days, a dog park for furry friends, and trails for those who love to explore the great outdoors. Brand new elementary school is scheduled to be completed soon and located in Ventana.
